overview: You've got to work hard to get ahead. These boys get hard, give head, and get butt-laid. Interviews are tough, and the best boy gets the job. Will he do whatever it takes? How to impress your co-workers? Show them you aren't afraid to put your whole body into your work. Everyone needs a little down time in the boy's room. These boys need to get down together. Every office has a bully, but don't get intimidated, get intimate.
title: Office Twinks 6
